snippet.title: For Evelyn II - Shards of Creation | Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2248960/For_Evelyn_II__Shards_of_Creation/ 

For Evelyn II is a captivating adventure RPG in the magical world of Aura. Rich story, handcrafted 2D/3D environments, classic adventuring, choices, and retro pixel art. Explore, level up, and immerse yourself in an unforgettable journey where your decisions shape your destiny.

Support: https://www.patreon.com/kisuarts 
Follow: https://twitter.com/Kisuarts 
Links: https://kisuarts.carrd.co/
